# Project 1: Times Table Practice


## User Story

AS A parent
I WANT an app to practice time tables with my child
SO THAT she can get better at it

## Features

Learning Mode
* Select the table to be learned
* The times problems are displayed till the student gets it right three times
* A sticker (GIPHY API) is awarded when the student finishes revising a table
* Keep track of problems that student gets wrong and ask them again
* Play a video of a song for the particular times table (Youtube API) if the child wants to learn the song
* If the user gets the table wrong more than [] times, they have to watch the video

Testing Mode
* Take an input of the range of sums to be tested
* User can select a timed test or a test consisting of a fixed number of problems
* Some award based on the score is given to the student
